data.description: Looking for a home with lots of space, great views, a pool, AND is close to the lake? 8518 Nesting Trail has it all! With over 4000 square feet of living space, this home has plenty of room for your whole family. Gorgeous vaulted wood ceilings with exposed beams in the living room over looking the mountains in the distance. Massive kitchen with 2 pantries and seemingly endless cabinet space. Relax in the huge master bedroom complete with fireplace. Also on the main level is a formal dining room, a second bedroom, and laundry room. Head up one of the 2 stair cases to 2 more bedrooms with jack and jill bathroom, huge bonus room which could be 5th bedroom, and even more storage. Outside you will find the in ground pool with fence and a variety of flowers all over the property (more pictures available upon request) Looking for low maintenance? Most of your major items in the home have been addressed.  Updates include: 2019: exterior was painted. 2020: interior was painted, septic tank was pumped, pool pergola was added, roman shades in living room, reflective window tint on living room windows added, kitchen cabinet hardware changed, several ceiling fans and light fixtures updated. 2021: New combo HVAC unit for downstairs, new coil on upstairs unit, new motor on pool pump, new sand in pool filter, and more!  Call today to schedule your showing!
